WEBVTT

00:02.592 --> 00:09.063
In Japan, International Olympic Committee chief Thomas Bach and Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe...

00:09.573 --> 00:15.246
...reached a preliminary deal to postpone the Tokyo Olympic Games until 2021...

00:15.481 --> 00:17.967
...amid overwhelming international pressure.

00:19.399 --> 00:21.721
In India, Prime Minister Narendra Modi...

00:22.183 --> 00:27.507
...ordered a 21-day lockdown of the world's second most populous country on Tuesday...

00:27.961 --> 00:30.013
...to halt the spread of coronavirus.

00:31.691 --> 00:33.071
Authorities in China said...

00:33.383 --> 00:39.226
...they will end a two-month lockdown of most of virus-affected central Hubei province at midnight,...

00:40.016 --> 00:43.741
...as domestic cases of the virus continue to subside.

00:46.005 --> 00:55.131
Deaths from the new coronavirus in Iran rose by 122, bringing the toll to 1,934 fatalities,...

00:55.405 --> 01:01.687
...Iranian authorities said Tuesday, as the worst outbreak in the Middle East continues to unfold.

01:03.499 --> 01:10.239
Finally from Britain, home appliances firm Gtech, which specializes in making vacuum cleaners,...

01:10.916 --> 01:13.497
...has made a prototype of a medical ventilator,....

01:13.992 --> 01:18.652
...which founder Nick Grey says can be scaled to mass production within weeks...

01:19.029 --> 01:21.527
....to help in the fight against COVID-19.

